OL,3,CBelfast Harbour to invest #1.3bn over
OL,4,Cnext 25 years
OL,6,FBelfast Harbour has announced a 25-
OL,7,Fyear investment plan worth more than
OL,8,F#1 billion to further strengthen the
OL,9,Fcity's position as a leading "maritime
OL,10,Fgateway".
OL,12,FThe plans claim to support 5,500
OL,13,Fconstruction jobs and underpin an
OL,14,Festimated #12 billion for the wider
OL,15,Feconomy.
OL,26,@rD@HO]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G1/12
