FL,444,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44306
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F443A1779307555
OL,3,CBelfast Harbour to invest #1.3bn over
OL,4,Cnext 25 years
OL,6,F"I fully support this vision, which
OL,7,Fpromises to significantly increase
OL,8,FBelfast Harbour's contribution to our
OL,9,Feconomy and regional connectivity,"
OL,10,Fshe said.
OL,12,FTheresa Donaldson, chair of Belfast
OL,13,FHarbour Commissioners, said the
OL,14,Fharbour "has served the regional
OL,15,Feconomy for nearly two centuries".
OL,17,F"The port is not simply a feature of
OL,18,FNorthern Ireland's economy ` it is a
OL,19,Fcornerstone of it," she said.
OL,26,@nD@AOUqD@cO]vD@IOUwD@aO]yD@AOU{D@SO]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G6/12
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,444,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44307
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F443A1779307555
OL,3,CBelfast Harbour to invest #1.3bn over
OL,4,Cnext 25 years
OL,6,F"This masterplan sets out a clear,
OL,7,Flongterm vision for how Belfast
OL,8,FHarbour will continue to deliver
OL,9,Fgrowth with purpose over the next 25
OL,10,Fyears.
OL,12,F"It is the result of two years of
OL,13,Fextensive engagement, and I want to
OL,14,Fthank the customers, tenants,
OL,15,Fgovernment partners, and members of
OL,16,Fthe public who helped shape it.
OL,26,@nD@AOUtD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G7/12
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,444,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44308
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F443A1779307555
OL,3,CBelfast Harbour to invest #1.3bn over
OL,4,Cnext 25 years
OL,6,F"Their input has ensured this plan is
OL,7,Fevidence-based, ambitious, and
OL,8,Frealistic, reflecting our
OL,9,Fresponsibility to the economy,
OL,10,Fsociety, and the communities we serve."
OL,12,FMs Donaldson also said that delivering
OL,13,F"a plan of this scale requires true
OL,14,Fcollaboration" and the Trust is
OL,15,F"committed to working with all our
OL,16,Fpartners to navigate the strategic
OL,17,Fchallenges that sit outside our direct
OL,18,Fcontrol"
OL,26,@nD@AOUrD@gO]uD@AOUvD@NO]wD@AOUzD@HO]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G8/12
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,444,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44309
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F443A1779307555
OL,3,CBelfast Harbour to invest #1.3bn over
OL,4,Cnext 25 years
OL,6,F"For port projects, a key priority
OL,7,Fremains the reclassification of
OL,8,FBelfast Harbour's accounting status,
OL,9,Fwhich would allow us to borrow
OL,10,Fprudently to fund critical
OL,11,Finvestment," she said.
OL,13,F"Without this change, we can still
OL,14,Fdeliver, but we will face harder
OL,15,Fchoices regarding the pace and scope
OL,16,Fof our work.
OL,18,F"With it, we can go further and
OL,19,Fprepare for the scale of growth that
OL,20,Fboth the economy and our customers
OL,21,Frequire."
OL,26,@nD@AOUsD@LO]uD@AOUzD@AOU}D@IO]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G9/12
