PN,44310
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F443A1779307555
OL,3,CBelfast Harbour to invest #1.3bn over
OL,4,Cnext 25 years
OL,6,FJoe O'Neill, chief executive of
OL,7,FBelfast Harbour, said: "Much of what
OL,8,Fpeople and businesses across Northern
OL,9,FIreland depend on passes through here
OL,10,Fevery day, from food and fuel to
OL,11,Fconstruction materials and consumer
OL,12,Fgoods.
OL,14,F"Ensuring that trade continues to flow
OL,15,Fefficiently is our core purpose.
OL,26,@oD@XOUvD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}           G10/12
