FL,444,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44311
SC,0011
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F443A1779307555
OL,3,CBelfast Harbour to invest #1.3bn over
OL,4,Cnext 25 years
OL,6,F"As capacity tightens at key ports on
OL,7,Fthe Irish east coast, we are putting
OL,8,Fthe scale of our estate to work
OL,9,Fproviding the planned capacity the
OL,10,Fisland needs, supporting customers
OL,11,Ftoday and preparing Belfast Harbour to
OL,12,Fbe the principal maritime gateway on
OL,13,Fthe Dublin`Belfast Economic Corridor."
OL,15,FCatch up with the latest UTV Live on
